videos.description: Rhode Island's Cyril Langevine gets a huge block then runs the floor for a layup after a nice behind-the-back pass from Fatts Russell.
videos.headline: Rhode Island gets it one on both ends of the floor

videos.description: Fatts Russell attacks the rim and gets and-1 layup to fall for Rhode Island.
videos.headline: Russell converts tough and-1 layup

videos.description: Dayton's Obadiah Toppin jumps above the rim to grab the lob for an alley-oop slam.
videos.headline: Toppin gets way up to throw down alley-oop jam

videos.description: Fatts Russell finishes fast break for Rhode Island with a layup.
videos.headline: Russell nails fast-break lay-in

videos.description: Trey Landers just misses game-winning putback shot as Dayton heads into overtime vs. Rhode Island.
videos.headline: Dayton can't get game-winner to fall, forces OT
